---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import bgImage from "../assets/slides/cusco-magico.png";
---

<Layout
    title="Página no encontrada | Expeditions Group"
    description="Lo sentimos, no pudimos encontrar la página que buscas."
>
    <main
        class="min-h-screen relative flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"
    >
        {/* Background Image with Overlay */}
        <div class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full z-0">
            <Image
                src={bgImage}
                alt="Fondo Cusco"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                format="avif"
            />
            {/* Darker background overlay for better contrast */}
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-[4px]"></div>
        </div>

        <div
            class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-4xl px-4 text-center text-white flex justify-center"
        >
            {/* Glassmorphic Card Container */}
            <div
                class="bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-14 border border-white/10 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden w-full max-w-3xl"
            >
                {/* Large Background 404 - Text Stroke Effect */}
                <div
                    class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-[10rem] md:text-[18rem] font-bold text-transparent stroke-text select-none pointer-events-none z-0"
                >
                    404
                </div>

                <div class="relative z-20 flex flex-col items-center">
                    <div
                        class="inline-block p-4 rounded-full bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 mb-6 animate-bounce-slow shadow-lg shadow-white/5"
                    >
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            class="h-12 w-12 text-secondary drop-shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(234,179,8,0.5)]"
                            fill="none"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                stroke-width="1.5"
                                d="M9 20l-5.447-2.724A1 1 0 013 16.382V5.618a1 1 0 011.447-.894L9 7m0 13l6-3m-6 3V7m6 10l4.553 2.276A1 1 0 0021 18.382V7.618a1 1 0 00-.553-.894L15 7m0 13V7m0 0L9 4"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>

                    <h2
                        class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 drop-shadow-lg text-white"
                    >
                        ¿Perdido en el mapa?
                    </h2>

                    <p
                        class="text-base text-slate-200 max-w-lg mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-8 drop-shadow-sm font-normal"
                    >
                        Parece que el destino que buscas no se encuentra en
                        nuestro itinerario actual. Pero no te preocupes, el
                        mundo es grande y tenemos muchas otras rutas para ti.
                    </p>

                    <div
                        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center w-full"
                    >
                        <a
                            href="/"
                            class="px-8 py-4 bg-secondary text-white font-bold rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-black/30 hover:bg-secondary/90 transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-secondary/30 w-full sm:w-auto min-w-[200px]"
                        >
                            Volver al Inicio
                        </a>
                        <a
                            href="/contactanos"
                            class="px-8 py-4 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/30 text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1 w-full sm:w-auto min-w-[200px]"
                        >
                            Contactar Soporte
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        {/* Decorative elements */}
        <div
            class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-32 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/90 to-transparent z-10"
        >
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    .animate-bounce-slow {
        animation: bounce 3s infinite;
    }
    @keyframes bounce {
        0%,
        100% {
            transform: translateY(-5%);
            animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.8, 0, 1, 1);
        }
        50% {
            transform: translateY(0);
            animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
    }
    .stroke-text {
        -webkit-text-stroke: 4px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    }
</style>
